			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">输入冲击电流过大容易导致整流桥失效，峰值电流不超过150A，NTC阻值太大会影响效率</p>
			</text>
